AZING. Staff was WONDERFUL and smiling and made me feel so welcome. I had the Kalbi and it was DELICOUSLY AMAZING. OMG. Going back for more the rest of the week. HIGHLY RECOMMEND. PLEASE PAY THEM A VISIT, YOU WILL NOT BE DISAPPOINTED.\nUpdate: 2nd visit was just as EXQUISITE as the first. Had the Feijoada Special with beef. Everything is INCREDIBLY DELICOUS. And such a WONDERFUL staff.\nUpdate: 3rd visit was EXQUISITE. Got the grilled shrimp, OMG IT WAS DELIGHTFUL. INCREDIBLE flavor.\nUpdate: 4th visit, JUST AMAZINGLY DELICOUS AND CONSISTENTLY GREAT MEALS.\nUpdate: 5th and last visit for now. FIRST THING, THE STAFF IS ABSOLUTELY WONDERFUL, FRIENDLY, LOVE THIER JOBS, GREAT WHOLESOME PEOPLE. IT HAS BEEN MY ABSOLUTE PLEASURE TO EAT HERE EVERY NIGHT. Could not have picked a better place. THANK YOU TO ALL OF YOU FOR MAKING ME FEEL APART OF THE FAMILY.\nPlease think of opening a location in St Louis.....lol","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1d0nmHq2jNpRQvQ5fxrR7YcX51X4zlmDDsSBJdrL2iZ2msqpZKdEW0otNi59MNvwMdP0QfRJNjuISjmbGfHFxT8ggRZB2LSg42qajd8b3JAxNL6u2oNJqcUvLcPqptkgDK02f2P-rvFUY=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1HbjOQlU7SzEL4cdrCgPyrea_0Gu6IEyosvRJrHy9yn1KkriZLNyZRKctbIljFLHVk-B6zGg9PKhXa-AJ8BrVkjXxE-oCCKLTop309fdhHzZLDdT-CchAs5KRKt62tbXiYJg0ClffcCXSB=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0iCND7OfE8jHP-fBQPCcujPlCDIhvIqcq5W8KUJ_V5fR_9UfTshfdmLcVNw-y6CaxELb5OClYQgY_tWTGzTRRLcTP62NYx14Y_wGh7P-thcQBa-r0nu1K5UrOvMRFolpqGZL36iJ43IMy8=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn33OzG3t7O93lOcIa53v77FrdvZN7mfLwQqC0wp06zFbdKZNMRKL-QWfbdqivwdP0TcMARH0WINss15RO6llw-MzhzsdtV05gQ-h1A8ZqrQPo62BI_KWwdODfqc_DR3_F7jjoNZFeBhIQI=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2Z7jT5MEqSNdMAwo4iZpsjNXF1ZL26OV2Jfde9timR8BJLsZcXRKoCMgwAZoBCnLTnEzzlLkGCdumLWMLnnWU4Nn7BvrEgLiHVksAM1s8SQndUZLw0gC3WO9HFxGZyKNwy5M4rCHu8a9Ql=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1FdpVGLce7RJAOhjrtg3TncMZizCmko