inery so we got to enjoy food that paired perfectly with each glass of wine.\nThe staff is also amazing and makes sure that you have an unforgettable experience. This is definitely the place to go to celebrate a milestone birthday, anniversary, or other event.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2FyzeLPw5wrKslHM9YQrZw4QpXUrLwxBA9IQzfED2iFbky1HSh4CwFDm1Gu0_nPV7RKXs5bIkjvCubcfYRnzeUH2tEp5TGY2C88N9CzK4Hr69kUVf_cqn375qe4QQSSYj-yIx8=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3jrUGxpkm9jyEczP4t2DihNsZC47H-qcj5fRKYm-lYp9ftTG65SQvlm3YoQ8C4Tll16HzOMVQNjKyO3eUkwBmUxYttJwgyG9aqfD15lkmGH0F-F6nDRO3auHhuSvuxB0h7qsxo=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn26Hiv46zcU7BxrteD6sfRi0g5vaF8hJLFu7W6GKykzxUXd7DYR_cOoH0NP3eaXE5xDXUEvogd7Uzjo-WyfXtD-RYVszbprngJBxWX41OuyNbP2bIgUDY2WJoUkc9bodl1BTxvZGw=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1bvMenP2N_nHRRTwcbAbhfR4TYOUTN5McdF-YZt14uGmIu4-33lz5KiKZUGa4YzI5o3-1MwlumrRMunvTjykJzssDcjVeKmVaGaJpMf7rhzsz7yUiTolCCUu9F-b4WLLSas9i8=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0FUy_XoKCNRx_rA0_KqHvnVDvwfu3N4O32M7mJkC_zi1k5JW2Bv8MQp-AVN6kegCMVUSXVysjHDmogVeWNHsF-lVXfmomvX3E-bWs0ThRM_7QgeVV3IvvWyqnRLFSQpLYt7OgdWA=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn22Lmuup-EQucOQXLr1izllUbSOb2JirkMy8Ix-AGx7rn8iAvGutE1O6R8Xf3e2xMWuc6oZAHXVcw909PhEbAj0AKe0tUelgayFEL1Cfh3_KAQtY2E9fqv6xtSwp3hVWPp3cSqU=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0s4nLoX6y9-xRAZU3tTJ5hegpkzbSd5-mnMF6HRBWgLyU-RTDG4KUVlsU4naq2VqrfQihrhThrvZB8cbwrq0TgQBTwltRlSodtPurBnLTd4WYY8w4qBJhEEMYrL4gQTWEdAb3V=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0ygMBzvcscv2YXnoPJVNwp-gefXJ4FGRHoPDnV1bifhlRZSv7WzmhoECWO2hgwaFBVw2PNvdYhZuaqDgXWihJluDKedr72T3EfE06gOXcBaUwpQjnq0SE5J6BBSEfVAu6LL4CH=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1vHlyMOy0NJMGmoEKrySvrF7F1eBktNxnZrDl8V2oCg6mw8Ye4lm6XaAlFx0WarCQcdREglhzD8kGQT_Dd0zcg5fDsPGP9JoUN501GMEQNdf4FSMpE5sxIIyZwGrALYAMB16L3=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0zQKfrDBqrd6arr_MztNticQ2XPuOJOpHtpC4QwHPznL7VmyODjRDrKGQ_UlM9E-FotvYdpi-puZy4mI88d6HD-_1RAR4tV9Nuz0zJzCaiGcaFRx4uG8G2TLAxKNCPIUGCtP0A=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn11iDCaoRkGqBbO3KnHhKDAoDiYiz9axAxESSvVtKwFrhNyaqwQTwUDLh67LcnSvc5YXcQx4zWC9-Ygz2asAWRJkb-wDnz-JKBmTn6Flt5ahDdwobfcjzyVYUTjh-Rh_-xk-NAe1Q=k-no"],"When":"2025-3-23"},{"Name":"Ayan Chatterjee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKStognldf-DqTKv80Khyikn5HyKn0Sh_T3Q1_faqYK9cMqmA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I have been meaning to check out Herbfarm for a while now. Found the service and atmosphere really good but not sure if it merits 5 stars. However, at the end of the day, we are there to dine. For us, we feel they fell short given the high price point. The wine selection was great but it felt that the wine was the star of the show, not the food. The small plates were tasty but not mind blowing. But the portions were just too small for the price. I mean two tiny pieces of prime beef, a small prawn floating in the soup, and 4 tiny pieces of American guinea hog was all the meat we got. For the price, we expected more. For people who prefer wine over food, or perhaps prefer eating less, this place may be a great choice. But for us, there are similar places in the Seattle area that are cheaper, more portions, and delicious (Juanita, Altura, Ltd Edition Sushi).","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1rru9En_nAUsKCqOsqCQSovGmTkG2DgCLR-fGu9HbBq44n4rc0ZUhJD8Wy8JS1YX46ZF50203fv9jak5bD2_bwOCZUBt9dUV5sGNSS6q3pfWnQidgDEIZFZiGu05RXFkg1SS3ESLagIvlj=k-no"],"When":"2025-9-6"},{"Name":"Maxime","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJvQonM_vKr328wwRCPsGJ27Do5TnHFcfqkQjrjaXmWLruLyko=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We were 5 family members, celebrating a birthday.\nJust an amazing experience, right here in Woodinville, WA!\nThe chefs are culinary magicians, and so passionate about quality and provenance of the food.  That dedication shows amazingly well in the final outcome of all the elaborate dishes.\nService was impeccable!\nAtmosphere is warm and inviting!\nDefinitely deserves a Michelin star!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cindy NextOfCin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUZvZFGvggXDDApFruCMytZfP-Up9GN12sXWlkXu6abC8omCMU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been to chef tasting menus and Michelin star 1-3 restaurants all over the world. The herbfarm ranks as one of the best non Michelin places I've been AND it was better than some Michelin restaurants we've been to. It was such a special experience. From the time you come in to the very end. No detail was missed.\n\nWe arrived early to hear discussions with the chefs about the fresh ingredients grown at the farm. We were greeted with some hot cider and seats by a fire.\n\nWhen being seated we were led to a table with individual personalized frame with our names on it. The table and entire room was beautifully decorated. We had printed out menu booklets explaining the menu and wine pairing.\n\nThe chefs took some time to introduce all of the staff and also explain the courses and wines we had coming this evening.\n\nLast the food and the service was impeccable. Each course was incredible and seasoned to perfection. Not overly salted or too powerful. The staff was so friendly and knowledgeable.\n\nIt was just a perfect experience. I can't wait to go back!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1J6Fk2NY9MZotvz3y3fWHgFehz8hRU-Q6-iiMojBnEbLiSBaCZNMFCnL95arLL2pCf6MRCdVV1Dbxy4CIJ1OX_vz24tmsVj-zRgHmIkP9RSrfaUG0gsN4B76bFp_DhQwZztx7kcA=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1Rfng5AorEBNQlh1hMR8mnegbo0YVsbZMdIhBo-aItmHfNeQkkI2XDZVxklDKP3vByWYTHLu8uADrbdna4Zb62H82DaJ_fulJ6abqiwnV775AatFjRknFc8ZoJxX4Y-VnzSyva=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1OXzG3xpH7aB5DN8SDRmZqra