 small, as well as the sides. They explain what is in each sauce when they take your order. We ordered our burgers and my husband's onion rings were cold. I saw them bringing the tray with our lunch and then turn around and put it back in the window. Not exactly sure why. They did offer a GF Bun, by UDI's, and I did order with that bun. I was less than impressed when it started falling apart as I was eating it. The prices were high and we didn't order any drinks or soda's. Our bill was near $75 for the 2 of us and the food was forgettable. It will be a long while before we go back, IF we go back at all.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2DXogMkqb6c6Kop4HCk9mT-V02qgfjmUNK9YTy6sH4tMNChN3zr9b1t8PHtlI_qKDSBT4PCvMG2gjZ_YpUtYw4nuhd2qxOY9qCnkV19In87bxWu5OdwHPJuUsQxevcnIb7vup1DxPJv-lG=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3o69WBjt3zd91waq04ywkyBkBjlJ7PaqRNf07tQJLNn2-67dIrkvn45VQ4KxD7WAtuqln1H7OPcWtbSAtI_xuifyEeOT22gw5hsalGpXARDMxpsQ5j2CBbBsjBhjaW-6VQaJnsQPSWjsUN=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0RfLXyGIcQ_2mNWrmIoOiUuQuYWHSaqdlHQFXfJ5dSbraXrZ-R0zrdvYcM7FzEOtUSZevA0U-924Px5OtHgYGtS8y1EOCI2aH3XqUrD8IVKKq0ORVpPScZtMqdb8N-hNKyuOA6RXT0yuo=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn36Dk0OVLJ48goJLO97YGPcKtaH2Nxl6ZnaXFTrzfM5iQXdWQ9DuyMTEcTOOWY2ErQ0UXJCQmKZ642DGXdYKfhhzUzHjqDcATW1QMdDLiYkaZMlnKdDkGg8DTsTD363r7ccRrJDLlLtwpuf=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1GxcW0zhc_P6Z0PMKj5mVvTKwKXHxKDzz_Wtu6Ft5yjYF3eRTAPRZwSssYVkWHnskufPz303zPHrufZsNuGapckTGvZTCfxtFgELb33R6Q0_UfwMKjk5fFbtAjKeTF7v4QWQ3IHGFRh3v_=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0cSQz09B9MKhOinicr0kZ82PaPDTxYoT5BSFWgvAqUwJwEyHz4xh264KPILmEsU8giC98B45VPPQ1IGcS8o-se0l5amuNMnr7MyAKIXp7O_aK8OWHmj28zReTeYz3Hty2W_eRhGMaJ3QM=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3v8MpHfFvUR_yUVj64cyek0rzxT9xmxTUakyffAQNTsN1KZJSbmt8-5K9hm4uAkb0eDeqGIP4CQsYQIcmuC85ddR2loZdbQQmnEjP7051Hx9r_xB5ZuD67JW--1sNzVPF4ASLeak