MTadXtjbAf9ZWGRsmROdHhVKSzCGQKc8SYgTBZyLFRiz0Ptm4rDn4PTKLrQWxkl5BUbmAIkX_Yoe3oaFFz_nlTsw8XSXdw-YhYoy5A=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3xbdFRUtA5YA1fvzHkKNjctk95-ao8wNw9QNShahBR4hFyMCx_jT4qQwjvw1UrWvXtQS_UHJKEIoE-rCKBpBMn0HY4b5shrAMfTh3xNcIjHkvRZWWmsPqGX5ocVDW8FqPi4Xs9Awwy7zI=k-no"],"When":"2026-3-4"},{"Name":"Kevin Cameron","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVZqiZ2U2i8T7Ofk2iNDxyTK1yr0CZsE5CLC4_oG2l-fJqW47_CmQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had an outstanding anniversary dinner with my wife. We had dinner and then breakfast the following morning. I'm vegan and had two dishes. Altered: the Korean tofu skewers, and fried cauliflower steak. Both were well seasoned and very flavorful. The following morning I had two small items: vegan sausage and avocado toast. The avocado toast was better than most- the bread was soft but still chewy, not hard and crusty. The the avocado micro greens was pretty standard but also had what I think was togarashi and perhaps yuzu syrup which was sweet and citrusy.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0IglJB9qQEbdAOSC3hws6qx7763BO7yTNVM7u8H_eWAxSrABXqMfYymZCuU07VsrQWtVNsd4PjMxVdR7hNQbW-A5X_V1vWjRoBQh6kI5CMh7sTG2qDZXaJjM64Us_ucCSuC3iOwABb2tzo=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3G3VbI-ywprLQVxyB-vCxkAy5DMHRVxMSb8Hud5vQ0hjRnGf8FPLFkqPGHfh4VbHojWKasRd8cnLxhRNOafgo2CdlgB31E1e5063hB5xHffW-bi3lFnMXdiaNXcqNrbW3thlTPA7Y0nqII=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3DxTGDmrxkdEp9vmhrjDFJHZP3eJk4g8jCrYts-e5GQyTMKOMCb3dC1h0Fe7EF9J3ZcRPr_mYatg3AN1jELrEiHUESj6EpP7q9mz9hoLwcLfMbEsxYKltKW02nBureBclYv_q990qh6CU=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0u8-ket1xPkOQ9-AT3b3LJVrG7Z-uoOVy_b5L4NQd66aNL-iRVlYXoL7eZiEZazaCPd65jRThn1Z4HJToq9iM644Y0bwK8wMRM9buYlglvnW-TSZFZteyQDj14ksUGExnyB-4-EPahKUk=k-no"],"When":"2026-3-2"},{"Name":"Daz Wilkin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVDwHGqHdLTB924cU0s7c_ZQ14tWCXOETNEtBXQP7o9Qr-NC6ACuw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"An infrequently visited but always enjoyable restaurant. I took a friend here to celebrate her birthday. We were looked after by Victoria who is great: attentive and let us enjoy our dinner.\n\nWe started with spoon-served amuse bouche and then shared the beet salad which Victoria thoughtfully plated separately for us. A good mix of golden and purple beets if slightly too little.\n\nMy friend ordered the pork which was a healthily-sized chop and came sliced for her to enjoy and with 2 bones to enjoy chewing the remaining meat. The pork was perfectly cooked and tasty.\n\nI really enjoyed the King Salmon. I'd asked it to be cooked slightly under medium as I really enjoy the \"just cooked\" texture and it was perfect. It came with beets and parsnips too.\n\nI encouraged my friend to try the apple pie gateau and the restaurant thoughtfully added \"Happy Birthday\" and a candle to it which I appreciated.\n\nI really enjoy visiting this restaurant. The food and service is always good.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2Mt7Fq738N8LxXvRtzf12A_iWGvoOWVqaZDWjki86O4e7wOkpqNJQXweOsQAkeYVfh3sfAep4koyU6_61n5vlrfMiazDFZgGFvkggR1XAZsSZv5hNNe92idgC_dF2fc75mZibTkLaMqow=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1brV7nBwDEXEcUtd5x0IBXiIHiRg6AewyrVacC1WMYuHu6_B6MAH_2ePOBk8N3TRA4YJm50oFzKGhMa1bKWYonEIWAZyHGbM7ItB1QRPH81J11bXyXEP_CN6qrd9QL44KC5OjxSpHCKjk=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2XTrcwx1BGZPZBansmjGucvHjxXNSu33i9MlFX15k8YQj563beO6qLDERLFUQ4mc0KEYgTH37tC1y2NmrVS3z98ADRZ9ArcIZ8pdR5bGWvYE96ieH2zgcDMFHJS-VCP7uTeKV79PrCcPA=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn05fWw3Paq0y09xb3nLAmjzI0WYj64C9Ko8TfkD1zwHKvZ_ZSXIvx2HXHRxITx3gtTDD7mHLzc7SbrNMrh7ebG8Jmbut7MBwGRHT4S0MRK4y_J5UmxESA73cMlWk1Sx_1QR07lCHXSTYhza=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0PNcZgeBH_6k7ZW937ROXQTcI0CuwZmJy_0Bt3QhBT6vv0NjVQ4RTu_uo_-wZyqjUN