abled":true}]},{"id":"crowd","name":"Crowd","options":[{"name":"Family-friendly","enabled":true},{"name":"Groups","enabled":true},{"name":"Tourists","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Accepts reservations","enabled":false}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]},{"id":"children","name":"Children","options":[{"name":"Good for kids","enabled":true}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Free street parking","enabled":true},{"name":"Paid parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Parking","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Kelli Thomason","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLnVBS8m8LmLWDNGKm2do1EfudSC6cFrpAD4ffPUMwvbVGW_w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Visiting the area and found this gem while taking care of an errand and so glad I did. The portions are generous and the food is delicious. While inputting my order at the self-checkout visible as you first walk in, I turned to a couple of customers waiting for their food and asked for recommendations.\n\nBoth gave an enthusiastic thumbs up to the Flaming Boar burrito, so that’s what I ordered. It was huge and served with a few slices of jalapeño on the side, which I didn’t need! It was slightly spicy already, though I noticed you can request less spice when placing your order. I would definitely order this again. Next time I might try the bowl for comparison.\n\nI also ordered the egg roles which were equally delicious and served with a side of sweet chili sauce. I couldn’t finish the whole burrito and two egg roles myself so had plenty for another meal.\n\nI didn’t realize I could’ve placed my order with a person, which would’ve been nice since I had questions about the menu. Because I saw the self-order station as soon as I walked in, I thought ordering there was a requirement. Luckily the informative and friendly customers sitting behind me helped me out! In case you have questions, walk past the self-checkout and there’s a counter to the left where you can place an order and speak with an employee.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3FQBJUcYsKtKiB7R_1ra_gSZWNzZHhU8QY1riWOYYXRZpk8iaodLWigDSucM1nVFtUQ7PMpCoODK1mGn64k03oF7q3KiKB9YRo5DUfKhL7ucGF3pSRiUDSLYfFarjHo84wxQ_qe81eAO9u=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0cHnXril6YxDbxULL-a1GsWmT3HJdf8SKmiF4IGWMeU3PmcGuUj5X41_nW4Pp2vv_hOtChKYgKZzRVz_Azm76Jw_s_3v_jnv9og66EYeDxyA5dVMv4QsU-tdHc4470GdHhVMBP--DcBSo=k-no"],"When":"2025-10-26"},{"Name":"Laura","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKkfeOf0JLqNr7taJjO4ABQeH6lPmILV1k7fMyJK_S5tHVmHA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"This place was a bit of a letdown.  Super hyped on social media and rave reviews.  Marination has much better execution of fusion bulgogi Mexican.  The meat is much better there and the sauces are better too. Nothing was bad, but it wasn’t amazing either.  The meat wasn’t great quality.  Pretty dry, and very small thin pieces.  Seemed like cheap quality and the texture wasn’t great.  Tasted like the overdone bits from the leftover on the grill. The bulgogi fries were smothered in a very sweet sauce and the meat was tiny little pieces that had little flavor.  Got the pork burrito.  It was massive, but didn’t wow me.  I probably won’t be back.  I’d go to katsu burger instead for a casual fast fusion food.  Server was nice but there wasn’t much service.  They just hand you the food.  Inside was clean.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2sfSNK7c_lP9TQipu4Fij1DHe80TOIfSEICqKmupc6jK0YF_oo3EZRYK5AP4fBrDxQdDBpdJ4H7C2tQI3ndyHH1Jh0mydLk4uyHAdw7vsl4DoCH2ryeCoNkv9ehtjyqaGRCHTaRYMARH8B=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3jBv4CS6Mck7eH4oX7TmgmjxBTa6IlBeUuD4f9_FMJ7GJaXGL-KAUVsT2UIRF3_23RntmXra39FOoX05Ll3qR9lMFYkD6d8OOLtZwgbhDcrKd1fAno6k7Pjr3xwU_kOMUsQUeEkt62pDq8=k-no"],"When":"2025-11-10"},{"Name":"Ace Phelps","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWU8iQcSFT6aAm43og1lnRMoPJfX7wRm90yXQoMFftm3M19AaI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I gotta tell you man whoever reads this, the bulgogi burrito is the best of the best a lot of meat a bit greasy though , but taste so freaking good. I just found this place and probably will get the food from here regularly just look at this beauty that I took 🤌😊","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0US_0mHDzbQwLcppkY08PvTRhc_lrMV2eVSg-UkLptYorAmS_eOyqd1q16ITLb-TLY1CptFmyfMHfSlYFDY_ijjVJLfwSC_P3tjGoqFfafzxtW_GDk28VspA2-YzIqiqZApyQceOBDzkjt=k-no"],"When":"2026-1-28"},{"Name":"Asif Ahmed","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJSAZbTXFwMSGu5a4AWAHe64Isjet05I6HnmpjyZxbCL0DEEs8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Good fusion food. Burritos are good size, it will make u full. Service was good too. Average wait time for food to show up. Overall it was good.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2E8kUcIg_k6s48w7nsMw5Gh6pouSg2-1mGaZPp_jWIMGbe8lKdHO6gYr1Riuht2G_QWQ2FxSQNQUYaMqJ3BwE6-D5bby91LY9_V4eT7S2yYc21FlsFISEk_FgXBTefPocaiqR6KAYwqxm-=k-no"],"When":"2025-10-19"},{"Name":"Kyle Brown","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXlz0OqRZo7q9HJnGQmGxIGHsDnaywMOg0gVmP7zfBEVQ0_4fKrIw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is a hidden gem for sure. I ordered the Bulgogi burrito. The price was very reasonable for the amount of food that was served. I had a family of 4 that all ordered different food and it was served within 5 minutes and all prepared fresh upon order. I am excited to try the other menu items. I will definitely recommend to others!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Outlier","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVxjEOCJEQ08YRiENZoZXof8NPMzE-fAi-8_l_SBfYzAOHI844w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I must say I don’t give 5 stars easily when it comes to food but in this case 5 stars is well deserved. Quick, and amazing food / huge portions. Going half on the Huli Huli chicken, bulgorrito, or whatever you order is more than enough for 2 people. Make sure and keep Chops in mind next time you are in the Lynnwood area and looking for a serious meal (huge portions a+ food) that’s fast and easygoing","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Oliver","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWCegfiAdPRvDlLh-RUVl5_xHd59R3JACWN0xVj3zQ_dKbN5plk8A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Chops has great food for a reasonable price (nowadays) and good portion size. They don't skimp on the meat. The various options from chicken, beef, pork, and fish are great. The good is prepared really fast. Parking is plenty and seating is sufficient. Service you can order via the website, the two available kiosks indoor, or at the counter with a human. The amount of sauce(s) tends to be a little too much for me and my wife. For the first time, consider ordering light or on the side. Both the burrito and bowl/salad options are great.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lu Zhang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIZFoAijlSesg0a7HjbBijhhdx7o3r6lZ-l91kkywHE_tre6Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"So good! Portion is huge. We had Huli huli chicken and bulgogi wrap. Both were delicious. Wish they could open a restaurant in east side. So much better than chipotle burritos","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0RiTLd0Kl9O7MKGjLkvDQSM58A8UXUPorLjmwKvE4vKuQm_vdeMBSXnDy-GLIcejPzswDloAzB9rJTI_TcyVLAijVnTxjE2d3imBRNiOTTxwaiChnhw9WsymIWf4jH7sELtP-O7-xEfTQg=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3XyYnh0P8sfuqLhtclJOwiq7oklaQu0hIXsM_5lGkq2vZdVzJnXcJ54LYThTaNCgovbZNNI3AQk557ypLtGujHr6QO_fD2DD7DzK0if7dhrEqATx3oBBxxWMF9M-fCXxe_HZTQulmyK4Zt=k-no"],"When":"2025-9-2"}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
