aL2dIIuhrZPww=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place deserves some serious kudos! We went on valentines night, during a sold out dinner. We arrived 5 minutes before our reservation and was seated promptly. Despite the full house our drinks, appetizer and food came out perfectly timed. Our server was very nice and attentive too!\n\nWe go out every valentines night and expect delays and hiccups due to restaurants being so busy. Maynard handled everything great, we had no hiccups and no delays. The food was delicious too! We will be back!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1anZApqU5gwoFAlE58xsYgTTMc7FJGgzOlHDNsK9h1-gpvw2lH802XJBYuoWSxXayq4v9lhBAHgvzsPujeJ_ghjPIQ1ARe5gx78fd1PXisif76gejuCot9s-IVTYZni0lVdo_UrNRvSGkr=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3ufjmJC_6Cj_iVH7T1OwjCu5kZwVooZwSNE0bsCoIuOYO4A9rRP2va4Q1y_f86OQKxEFForvLMr_GRDFxBIYQfHOYlokbrLDN5N75vmbB_wYokxGelMB49ecykGMzgufNBHq8fwY_szQca=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0l8_QX2Kw2Cb4-ndZ5Cq_-PWzUkBItJ1C_IqNVcpVEHAE78xH04bzhXTC4aXex-Ry1YFBsdSJ5zkwr6X0k0qdwzhpEBvxXvojS2A3e225dJmaJ869qyYN2eMGpU1S5yF-9v5XG1JX7l6PY=k-no"],"When":"2026-2-18"},{"Name":"Cynthia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKZ80Bql4uDZh8SaQxHTb-8JYCOSh2_LWbVmm8bWqRyFGt2EA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We come to Maynard’s at least twice a month. The food is awesome, the service is so friendly and courteous. And the atmosphere is like a super high-end restaurant. They have a special for $25.99, which gives you an entrée, appetizer, and dessert. The smoked beats are Amazing, with They’re awesome balsamic vinaigrette and cheese mixture. I don’t usually like beer, battered cod, however, I enjoy theirs. As their beer batter is not too thick. They do something to their fries, which makes them super crunchy outside, but soft inside. My boyfriend loves the shrimp cocktail, appetizer and steak and mashed potatoes entrée. It’s always cooked to perfection.  I don’t even get me started about the dark chocolate flowerless torte! Heaven on a plate.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1tjCSb3eh2lh7MTS3obfgynkJ6Oim9eIGnCH5WSfqKCn39s7H6eFrkY40bljQkz3MlyD-9HBFpaXSTN3XBTmbMQCjKTkgH5Rouo9qpdOZA0GwErSQWrzarPj4yGBIXL63jZmW-jh7fVDY=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1MdXhUlhqE6EcqNSaQkpQBreW6D5JSBntl7ZeY8fNLXk634ssmg-5stL1Z0xinfwoRgwyYhCXad5Nqn53cs-Xqp67Y6zgNK-Yr53yD1hCOiG93TWELQmtRNWjsWtMd5l50lK5ms2MwzdI=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3BxQ2MunxJ418QCAsPTz-3Tq7QxEwj_mpTZkrTlVvC9XuwDIVeEUNtvznx9Msl4GRNPhmbLyFfv6NEWZT8H_JZaVTCKgKtlWuUTvvpFpn-6BiDLqTpU2e09vy5tGHwGBYZ3trXMOkOPfQ4=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0qTpuf_RighEfCBfLS4LzIBd7wF-QN3Guwno8otI1v_e0CtCObC2KDKcU5RTzc_5nc1FLvMwElcQ3JtktJIszwX_LWMlhJP2la1KDNk2VBwq4qKwvA1U03lKqGdgNQHEzXsvlXlv7xubaA=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1PVBBw77-SfuLRHXRFwnhiik2LqRchnDh0c4SFSm174o6nP1m_TeGdIFNHsNAdLB-MHJvtoYBHGpTMAf10lkh3Zb5-GCK0VPsWzuZGZCmP8kzwgr93Yi0QuUkd2vP_5Kaj7g0D7FAKRc7x=k-no"],"When":"2025-11-20"},{"Name":"Rhianna McDonald","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJaI1PNyo4XSR_34cFXU2FDdlkdECUy2kVqRvF9hsulaumX50xg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I can’t express how grateful I am that we found Maynard’s for our wedding event. We were eloping on Halloween but wanted a small reception a few weeks beforehand—a chance for family to gather and enjoy a beautiful dinner without the stress of booking a large venue or hiring caterers. Maynard’s made that possible!\nBethany, the event coordinator, was an absolute dream to work with—sweet, easygoing, accommodating, and helpful every step of the way. She let us tour the space, sample menu items, and even customize our own menu for the night (photo included). She allowed us to bring in our own desserts (photo included), provided cake-cutting ware, and gave us access to decorate the day before (a huge time saver!). She even made room for a temporary tattoo station (photo included) and a tarot reader setup in the back, and we could play our own music! Everything was so flexible and stress-free.\nThe dinner was phenomenal. Many family members commented on how great the food was, and one even said it was the best wedding meal they’d had all year—and they’d attended four weddings! We offered wine for the evening, but guests could still open their own tabs or visit the bar for cocktails, which was perfect.\nWhat amazed me most is that all of this was coordinated entirely via email since we’re not local. Bethany and the Maynard’s team made the process seamless and enjoyable. Truly, five stars aren’t enough. If you want an intimate, stress-free event with incredible food and outstanding service, Maynard’s is the place.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn21_Kvp-euwbhy3vbxx8KCAkXAnUm11uT7PEEPqAIpRga__0bWJJ9lubwi6-lYQIRcU57i7lRIIHnJgJGsqfxDZntLe14IiaZ37G2q1EisXpbnEOEJT8AFoJ5MBcohUUKYA5grSzB9dkMds=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn32RYQWVR6sBPRPLI1SDk7I9CScpCZZt8bianJNFAMXfRCis2NbeweQ5nfi1ZDNvcmig3cluqNPPZMlvk6FBcExeFaF2LwUvewdDx6Yudf-AWxZpNBwcqp4KRyUVsVoEIi0lhguO_h8UfAa=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn12iIGa2xAZaRJl8Fqx3R5QIg8SwIeT2sTaBOJucJSDb_GhcwVXfE7AQ9NQwzRxdpv39U6VwEhYGy8Z60a9eZrD6bD-WMB-lS8ZtE2v0wHQWrHbicp-qFpEz5Pdboo7nkQ0MGM_pR10aNx0=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0YzSZREpv9Mi-bWtrFLiYKYhP19ghCHvRH-j4ZTBVgdfbIa_t9ietaW1gNxQ0g4LSyM6oZYXkWvPyM2E84N9_YqjCjzIYKsTKAb-JDZXKpIJUhScaa6Z2K005O8fXAdmQf6kw5mXzJG0Di=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3jByHLzM832SnBVEkHrJ9UGvcO61PdZwooDwhHmOKh37DlatQh5qyBmRRiCp1pfEl8hmvmwzw_8HGH_mY26wegJYLcYgMpq46qQw6MY-GZNZgu8xl5gSxmOPnbcf9uy_2FA3L9EyvdxG0=k-no"],"When":"2025-11-10"},{"Name":"Jodi Daugherty","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV2zyhEXOkDdcR4wE7aR4eBgF4Srrdv3BL8IjoR2N9jvZ49oUJ2=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went here on a date night. Our time was later arriving about 7pm, so we were seated right away. Our server, Charmaine, was so nice and friendly. Gave recommendations when asked and checked in on us through out.\n\nWe ordered Spinach artichoke dip to start.\n\nMy husband ordered an Ocktoberfest Pretzel burger and I ordered their fettuccine alfredo with chicken.\n\nI choose their blacken chicken and though it was good, I think id do grilled next time.\n\nOverall, we will be back. It may be our new date night spot.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1fpDGXmHCKYbjuKT_O7W5WqNUdJUThHMi_K4viSYa4sG_kThFuqiV1Oo7XuywxiwtoTj_XMxUNOUFRa4_uXRsfuPTKTpQeMGL3yclfMieHHE9TxKyg6iT2QNEWrfktgG99YGDG49tPBMg=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2HagI3e1K_jTMnRLSCd3_yZ5GqTE0e6xRsLvOXQKz0P7t9YkD7Pd_qxY7kF1FjPdIZxlb2LfeMg_Rx-L90FfP0ezo-FYuApdV-eADoy6SXw3WuXtyYRc_Os2g9eBn9H_MXvNCW9wFUkFIy=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0bY06lKdYvnTBfesfnc6-NN9LBrO-LgE6qDEIvePJYpaef1orzLPcliR8ghiz8RC1gbVXUZs8xnOjLrpUP5F11ni4Cd3gnkyF0sAsT0AfP1PC7Yq0WS5NPtvh7JNNjtrQbArD02GRsBhb0=k-no"],"When":"2025-10-25"},{"Name":"Tim Meikle","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW1-L77m_iIW7HGlJIse9sRnshTWlMpJWQ7KF0GP8bJOaIuOrat=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Maynard’s Restaurant is truly outstanding. The food was absolutely magnificent—beautifully prepared and delicious—but what really sets this place apart is the incredible service.\n\nI first met Shannon in December when I attended a work Christmas dinner. She was our server and immediately stood out: fun, uplifting, knowledgeable, and genuinely funny. She made the entire evening memorable. Because of that experience alone, I knew I wanted to come back.\n\nOn January 3rd, I returned with my family to celebrate. Unfortunately, it was a very difficult evening for us personally. My wife had just received devastating news and was doing her best to hold herself together, and we also have a child with extreme anxiety who rarely goes out. Despite everything, we decided to keep our reservation.\n\nBy what felt like pure providence, Shannon was our server again.\n\nThat night, Shannon showed a completely different—but equally amazing—side of her service. She read the room perfectly and matched the energy we needed with compassion, patience, love, and understanding. She never rushed us, never made us feel uncomfortable, and treated our family with such kindness and grace. In a moment when we were emotionally raw, she helped create a safe, comforting, and welcoming space.\n\nShannon is an absolute gem and the kind of person who turns a restaurant into something far more meaningful than just a place to eat. Because of her, Maynard’s will always hold a special place in our hearts. We will absolutely be back.\n\nThank you, Shannon, and thank you, Maynard’s, for an unforgettable experience.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2DOUHD9WsITXZ4DmkQIL_2gHA7gNkulLR3FWWRMWSBd8p74THkqoxKCAtZ0zAkxrcEllkI1zRxUn9DaSCKmbK6abR75048VXG8jwGsRKPnWCnKi_xGDbUcn0vAm01-_Rt3uZ-ljHAzh4w=k-no"],"When":"2026-1-5"},{"Name":"Anika Wargo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXDt_7Y4kG7svvwpEsn8u1huYhzRTCPkCtHJ-vyWv9vPucM11Bm=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Inside of the restaurant was a very nice atmosphere with an open design and lots of seating. Huge windows with mountains in the distance. The kitchen is visible and you can see the kitchen staff working. Service was very prompt and professional, and our food came quickly. The food was delicious. It feels like going somewhere a bit fancy, but the prices for food are not much more than any other normal restaurant. The menu is simple and not overwhelming. We both loved everything we ordered.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1DZFhQIhXXSfmGmvLDX1i6-mSLKnpg5