erson, and I’ve also ordered delivery, and every experience has been excellent.\n\nFrom the moment you walk in, you’re welcomed with warm, genuine customer service that makes you feel valued and comfortable. The staff are attentive, kind, and always ready to help with a smile.\n\nThe food quality is outstanding — always fresh, beautifully presented, and full of flavor, whether dining in or ordering delivery. Even through delivery, everything arrives well-packed, hot, and just as delicious as in the cafe.\n\nClean atmosphere, great service, and consistently high-quality food all in one place. Highly recommended for anyone who appreciates quality and professionalism. I will definitely be coming back.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1J0Yn5gEokGXDEOgF8xc1FiWYqeBviK74LaoPayAi7lAfZGv1uSUD7tTQZ4GBYTG8jlJB1Z1E-qBozEOmRUtGwucr-GNukpTDcu5mnNz-5oq4tKfuMNbzr3SWU2uYTDPvC04zPwvIih7I=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3ESnQ3mn2cmbXRcBBn19PhPdS5cKOdvC9G-KvYXOY9KRyRmC--psOp_n3-LdPlDr99cpex4EVbIvufclSk9Xg94unKMVqHrCrWFIv63ftCfQLho2RQ0qOJ52hqzmUNYHNqvjinkJeRdIWA=k-no"],"When":"2026-1-27"},{"Name":"Isaac S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWXuxSFrpeuZu_kmAJ8g5MvQDgC2q-wEfdDlPR3AEb-xDCUFYQEBw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Noon Cafe is a lovely Persian restaurant tucked into an unassuming strip mall. I stopped by for lunch and was genuinely impressed.\n\nThe service was some of the friendliest and most authentic I’ve experienced in a long time, and the food somehow managed to surpass even that. Everything was delicious, well priced, and perfect for a midday meal.\n\nI ordered the chicken kebab, which came with a generous portion of flavorful Persian rice and a fresh salad. It was excellent.\n\nI’ll definitely be back to try more of their Persian dishes. It’s easy to see why they do so much Uber Eats business. I just wish I lived closer so I could order from them more often. Highly recommended.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0qOKO1kTQlzEP0QtTogFTVylrXpWTYVRla6lTQ4DdCzkeanMQx7YlBDf8XN58jfnMTrBSj5tN2D3yTjTsWmRihkQrA9RIfFb_Ck0LA-ULA7syOfGrBH8FWWEoLpSAZ4U283qR785yoq0Q=k-no"],"When":"2025-12-16"},{"Name":"Huda Khadair","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXOqZOu3vzUh76Wfh9BQ0JYssRBYPdNjwXQ-Xd9pGv916PLYL4t=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I ordered the chicken skewer and Kobidah and it was fantastic giving out 10/10, then we order the pizza and it was disappointing. It’s very oily, and the dough is very crispy and thin, I will not recommend the pizza, but the other dishes yes. It’s kind of expensive for two people $70. I will go back to try different dishes. The service lady is very sweet and nice.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2tfZ2fPDtoSDNqLdl_atiZ94NNR805CdGj26dSh8mvo-S8SjPmcJg43wHGPQaWDcs2QXXW0NC5RAhpxff87itAXBka0FaoaDPfkHr9ufYfPOJPqtmae6tgaF4roPDVufhFBz5j2izWRjU=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2Q9--RdBMihoRqd453FprfxgItW5LFL2Qa8TQegehHYzHMewk6y8R1JGNmX0m_gW8WXRg5W2kqF914AgWJ85c-B-4Kmu4kDyaGmiOjjy_T6thcqIvtqY0pjf5U5HtCaocVzW6MgZJ1yMc1=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0IUZ8ZEgLy_sb9IN8K9M4ZHd5m80neULeQiR3Hd94UleX4FHhLfoptu2WUiNWqmpZZFp1UZCwzM346hlQe2K26KzhU8ELFiAbNz6iq6arsnIo3hT9AOHiLjnfyadSk_Bf_sPbVEGcpS2ta=k-no"],"When":"2026-2-18"},{"Name":"Daniel H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVOBFkEcHYc5ClU33GZeXV_aBpV5iE_uz8M5Kx1BxDlLRhVmbiLlA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent spot for a healthy meal. Ordered take out two days in a row. First day ordered the one chicken kebab. It was a lot of food, juicy chicken and nicely cooked rice. Served with the basil, onion, grilled tomato.\nNext day had the ground beef skewer and the chicken again.\nThe takeout is fast and easy. One skewer for one meal. The two skewers turned into two meals.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn31Ri2Y8qpVYfb3dfVbfueWWshZPjWbEo9EB-W2DJ4W3cSsfScinE9jiFMPFh9efVex-s7yAqOE0zstSIbj6qJR12fUY_cbUpaHA6wp2OI30VzWoKdsajp7ZDk44kSV9iQmPlf0s38_GzpW=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0Od16W-T3i_yq6p1Nsup4-bc0E8-WvhXAULsUL8GFeiSEu78h_ABvXLSJSUewyVfwYyCBcurVtYnmUns9kG4HF29dpcFHs62kZkkyCcRRmx3ynQPXEXxWeWkqyfeZzKAVo5MVAf_nrr04=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0FtBj4GGUU6eaPgHyHF_kAk1e9pAjrcHKZaBNZJIhi2yvYsi2u0EVaHT9PFfpx4RhiX9Y4W1R40eiPQjEWQ0XF-Qqqy17uIIAtSBndEDGlx4QHGQVcw-yByF2K9csH5A7gQnBKMVhC25w=k-no"],"When":"2025-12-23"},{"Name":"Chelsie Martinez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKhJkt2ep1420iCMRt_yuloqJ0LqVOpe9XsvlWo6gntpiqqqw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My fiancé and I are so thrilled we came across this gem! The food was so flavorful and delicious, and the customer service was AMAZING. Some of the nicest people you’ll ever meet, and they were SO attentive to our needs; made sure we were satisfied the entire time! Wonderful experience! Would definitely come back when visiting from out of state again!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0YVjQe4NphFIFnJxm7uwscx6WbbKDERRo-Uks-G1D2paJPI2_oanYnYi_utOMs4lQHi4nbHKE5SIMG6ddW-edis3_nh72Xb41Hj-lc_ichSTnnv6cfiwjQXtTt0mTd-Ok4WJquFl8d4wVl=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2wX_rL4S5q7tjM6WVsPfKAXIN2Ht__hUxjhvQJdiXS0MFCTFJakBvbw2VuzqKWPW-pRxeHtNIhW-8Pwsv_CtmNC6uuomtWqygwRoITx0a8-TwBCWxmND2iW5iILNO61i5lcrMA5FdkftL4=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2SqRSbkq_rZ2kmipllwXVdwM_nwGCBj3ibuSVPYMuN4FQ3XrFDjMsngYa8NYZfSa0V9mt0zLuy0jgkZENBJeRZM5m5sJ4Grz0esxqugasnCO2DeFk3D-U1OwrZiP5IpOKxWEGTPyv4ojt5=k-no"],"When":"2025-8-12"},{"Name":"Calvin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ_5kmELRKp93OKU815rl00hsWTpRbensEtskuRrpOofQm-Pg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What a great finding! Get the kebab combo and skip the pi