\n\nWhat makes it special is the atmosphere: cozy enough for families with kids (complete with crayons and a kid-friendly menu), yet stylish enough for a date night or a gathering with friends. I especially love sitting outside on sunny days, under wide umbrellas, with the breeze carrying the sound of laughter and clinking glasses. Their patio near the bar is my second favorite spot—you can still feel connected to the world outside while enjoying all the comforts of a tavern.\n\n🍗 The Food Highlights\n•\tFried Chicken – I don’t even like fried chicken usually, but theirs is irresistible. Perfectly seasoned, always crispy on the outside, tender on the inside, and consistently delicious.\n•\tBeecher’s Mac \u0026 Cheese – Mac may seem simple, but it takes real technique. Hollywood Tavern has mastered it: creamy, soulful, comforting. It usually arrives baked just right, though on one visit it came out a little darker than usual. Chef—please note, your consistency has always been flawless, and that one time was the exception. I keep coming back because you’ve nailed it every other time!\n•\tFried Pickles – These are my personal favorite. Crisp, tangy, and addictive—even my loved ones, who doesn’t like pickles, devours them here.\n•\tWings – Golden, juicy, and paired with celery and ranch, these are tavern comfort food at its finest.\n•\tSandwiches \u0026 Burgers – Flavorful, hearty, and always paired with fries that hit the spot.\n\n🍹 The Drinks\n\nThis tavern takes pride in craft cocktails that balance creativity and tradition. Whether you’re sipping champagne in the sun, enjoying a whiskey neat from across the street at Woodinville Whiskey, or indulging in a house cocktail, every drink feels crafted with intention.\n\n⸻\n\n✨ Final Thoughts\n\nThe Hollywood Tavern is a gathering place that feels like home—welcoming, consistent, and full of heart. Whether you’re here with kids, on a date, or stopping by after wine tasting, this is where you’ll want to land.\n\nWoodinville is full of attractions—whiskey, wine, artisan bites—but this tavern is the soul of it all. The kind of place where neighbors meet, visitors linger, and families feel free. Cozy, inviting, and unforgettable—Hollywood Tavern is where Woodinville’s heart beats.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1UXgigHiRTHz4x5ghrkgjL4ZJdfB-KLqzUIXEzNpCoQtP_p8w9PDrnSEYRRs8TZuaXvBEBxZavkRT2GjcHm6bSnhmbg1Cmki4e8rvICCMPprB47K9nuzvGN6ukhmQawG6A0j6pQW9anTWK=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2_8_WH-_Dib0pGDwFJV6x8saywuQC8Ahqwv1qmyfqpISBMngJjocgGAUtXBLqfwIpMgqG8_kHPafIzI7Ocldr4FXSX6385dJIxzHOnaZxdWSXywWM2CUlCxszunxhzFfT2HuC79O2wvFA=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0yFp2wm79kPhuW39wl8HS_MhZQ3QBN3KguYIq-sS4aN-PyF13_dISqOHLjdxHrFDt5t993SeACrn2AypUs966UWOmo9Bz-6BgZy4OmFdGsizujOgC2HqW7_wvmcltI1B_K8GnIAHh-Y47q=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0a1yetVJT5XZGp_j9eqhiKhcA05SYXhkTCu0zPyezrTQkKnleDUb31-Y-T0uqaFMEw_9OXP5MwNC-i28waoECD0r9f5uMaaxe_LCS-p_Mts5C2Ki_h_ey1niNkU5GZZXcVulphoKxItTE=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2OevMguBBlLktDIYdq6fn3x55o3TKT3tcxo11yJwIuGwfceAaOMoCawQq6Oa0EM8jmAIKPcqDEUqguE12DKNvDXt6gK_x8NwK15oVhghzilUONXhHWKYIG4dGWto2uXSEWbXX4rvpi0FE=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn26qBYndoCJWZdH75ibbCRuK2K_hH8ynbHs3FrGtes6mg_m30jbOvonlLZFiIoFVJFOLvf1Qudcssyf9HHZtWWbefwfW2VtONaNmjDpbXM7a72WUa7jfZkJx_H2NDpvSUJM0AG2OGz8Llzs=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1ELU7Hzcm2iA7PdqHveYUKJ2dEzLFlh6T3csqDpYfSzz6LZVx9wIlwj0fGgsu2fRgFdoffEGpBJ1z00GEb8zSWyoHV0il70UpANbbK_ML6mQ69QOGEsezYMwwzWC3y2KkPHNEHX9URL4wT=k-no"],"When":"2025-8-23"},{"Name":"Stefan Vladiuc","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUTZ_PBqhGr3meqhh9e6aSRELeo89I7nb92ktP0sZmBKEVsl0YM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is amazing a small gem that I wish I had found earlier. Food amazing, place amazing, customer service amazing our server Mc