ng","enabled":true},{"name":"Parking","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Jennifer L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXPJ1uSa-y8mf-r4D48-NI5C4sUvMyYxwLgX9iL2RWu83HzVbSyeA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is so good, I can’t believe I’ve lived in this area pretty much my whole life and never been.\n\nWe sat at the bar and our bartender, Cameron, was fantastic. He gave the best recommendations, made great drinks, and was genuinely fun to chat with. He really elevated our whole experience.\n\nWe ordered a few bites like the salad, bread, steak bites, and burrata, and everything was solid and enjoyable. The favorite drink we had that we all agreed on was the \"Where is Sancho?\"\n\nKro Bar is easily the coolest bar in the area. We actually planned to do a little bar hopping, but after starting here, everywhere else was definitely not as great. The vibes weren’t the same. Kro Bar set the bar way too high and the rest felt pretty average in comparison.\n\nIt’s also a very small spot, so plan ahead. Make a reservation or go with a smaller group if you can.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2Zpt6jnZmY9X3tEnpub8FxeQielMrwdC7IytobwpmuNtjozS2O_gB1giRdb-ktPL59hL848F_2uCQmy-Uhx61XqtX7_ZqHVQFoWjnMH-CYghcSOU65y4T0z_WvZsH2yYMKuebTPuhNyA2_=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn10h14SQ4Ylq6YtUJqIbiQVvu6rkC1RGw807eHkCtOfjob0YGG6svOYPcpM5k_0RjEMrZesoHfEvlO9CcMXAHS5oPZRSaAnzulFqsZQs_ZvOLbTWve6al6Lk5P6pab15Ajm45PhQqxK7XjV=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3EUa9_uC58EkP_Qq6mXJPsOcNs0ttVdBCt8inOpyafNiJbDcmLbEimrm-9DGepaneRrEsji2APuudVz4FmxjHUHAwLNTzJNirNVuZvDmtfo6S3yWSLM75ySAIVtrW5rzT4p-MgUj3ibX4U=k-no"],"When":"2026-2-1"},{"Name":"May Wu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUYNJuwYR-p4RsSE4k2mLkIV5r1CngvxC6jAa4XEx4Kh0Dzz1wk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Kro Bar has become one of our absolute favorite places, and for good reason.\n\nThe drinks are consistently excellent - thoughtful, balanced, and clearly made by people who care about their craft. The food is honest and well-executed, particularly dishes that celebrate the character of the cut.\n\nOne thing that really sets Kro Bar apart is how much intention they put into their events. We've attended several prix fixe food-and-drink pairings, all carefully planned and genuinely fun. Just recently, we spent New Year's Eve at their 9pm-midnight party: a five-course, five-drink experience that was joyful, generous, and incredibly well run. It was our first NYE not spent at home being in town, and we had an absolute blast.\n\nBeyond the food and drinks, the staff truly make this place special. From the bar to the kitchen, everyone is warm, professional, and grounded. Even when faced with challenging situations, they handle things with grace and integrity, which speaks volumes about the culture here.\n\nKro Bar feels like a place built by people who respect their work and their guests. We always feel welcomed, taken care of, and genuinely happy to be here.\n\nWe'll absolutely keep coming back and recommending it to friends who appreciate good drinks, good food, and good humans.\n\nPlaces like this deserve support.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0qTqfAIHyG7PWjPVQLS7g-Sm7rCeLt8DtsJIMEqMycBkgxKakNjVxzY7WolqYaeiKdGgi80UgupCcCQ0vF-g48GbBSTCuwLs8R_AHaQixJrRoCF5Msa8cme7DFYbTaKAUveyApkz4uU5oY=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2HNBYOL-f1dvACu6mVgxiTYA5fVLp53B3EMuEfKYWrERdRyOL3j3mWp_W9_z7YUCEa5WQKCltdg8RjbL0-LLbVmHRQK_xA6Im-j_bbUpqbDd-ewZYW90CDbFJfzexY210lU79fy8jAwko=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3_aY5nIyEJSbOV3rFRqI8nm3qEBlWUiUc5mmN3Qii3ZsYyBNQ5WBBVDmFsoLAOLCw5xpDQAQ5BvvJ0xaMF7vef8EfGFNoFiHI2wLrf8bpMOpj4CuOMyLNMRx485N2LN-GklPnzdqDZM4wZ=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0Hl_T-x0hvHdZMEmaLQGUPvz2OPAkTQPDXjhenpR9ZZsAqipCCp7v67AR44pcXRPYiaf6bGJ