 and appetizers on the table within 10 minutes or so. I highly recommended a pork sliders they were absolutely delicious. My wife and daughter had clams, (which they raved about) the clam chowder soup was also great. My personal favorite which I try this meal in pretty much every restaurant I first go to was the classic Washington (fish and chips!\") you have two choices- either (halibut or cod) I choose the Halibut. What makes this dish so great and I loved it so much was not only the fish delicious but the sauce they served with it was absolutely delicious. The dish also came with fries which were thin cut which were delicious.\nIf you have never been to this restaurant I would absolutely 100% so you have to try it if it pulls well it's a fantastic place whether it's lunch or dinner. So it's mid to high price we spent about $150 for the four of us.\nEnjoy,\nJames...","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0R7TRt5POH268Mu1OcF-3QtA_Jo9ziY8vxUgEOQJ5aC6DY8YmQom8P4iUtFCNAVXI4HwM0D97UVNnk90HRnkgKRnMsVi4PAW-K4wW9OxPAN-j5r2qG_z8Ux0Az71gstbhHSbU4LjELaWeq=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1faLC8AkojQImpXTJgVy7SaGPwXTfLcaWOOBPgVXLfnBrZWbkH7YZuWsnvpQutiEp8B-4dlUyzTRcpn0wxwJ-YTzXjnMeaURQ95Ia1c_5xgE4hqWrk_BBgiYoOnUsWwPHEGk4on-_f_sGJ=k-no"],"When":"2025-7-16"},{"Name":"Adam Bursell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWcjpFGCK_I28XmL-6ZE2JtPuLcfHsiSRUhB2jNwtSOKxajw1sZ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Met some friends here, immediate seating, fast and friendly service from Emma - I think it was her first day solo. She did great. Had a fantastic black and bleu salad that was really tasty. Great views from the seating area. Nice relaxed atmosphere. Worth checking out!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1Hkfl7oiFbPBABEJaHU6csgjFVIT8-nUZ6WGo2FyzEU2N0jM1w2vT6rDJEmsEk1mxzyjfLvyFpXO3tvFFLnSiETAMuceOW7O2Jsrk58u93V5zrrd_hWxT0V0q6R9MUUM3aa6FKTD_a_UNf=k-no"],"When":"2025-7-25"},{"N