yle Korean cooking that tastes like it came straight out of a Korean kitchen. Every dish is expertly seasoned, perfectly balanced, and incredibly satisfying. The portions are generous, making it an amazing value, especially given the very reasonable prices for the quality and quantity you receive.\n\nWhat really sets Modoo Hansang apart is the consistency and care. The banchan are fresh and plentiful, the main dishes are hearty and comforting, and everything arrives hot and beautifully prepared. Whether you’re craving classic Korean comfort food or introducing someone to Korean cuisine for the first time, this place never disappoints.\n\nOn top of the food, the service is warm, attentive, and genuinely welcoming. You feel appreciated as a guest, not rushed, and the staff is always happy to help with recommendations.\n\nIn short:\n✔️ Authentic flavors\n✔️ Delicious, satisfying dishes\n✔️ Generous portions\n✔️ Fair prices\n✔️ Excellent service\n\nModoo Hansang is a must-visit Korean restaurant in Bothell and easily one of the best spots in the area for authentic Korean cuisine. Highly recommended — you’ll want to come back again and again. 🇰🇷✨","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2PjK1L7EKeicrN8KoBK5s5us6QNw1zYyIU757gzuhabJf93dK30Eizr-Plfo8leRpgZjnPw1L8sExymr_WP_ZtHWbsy1EJbZ0uG9OVcUb3EpO4stNpNETh1-ejMPlhyj0XgioZ3zgY8GWS=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0rPuXzWlRvwRrg7IpJfsGTDbPWbLvw4A3AUUQUs8mHxy75D1Iw7UpYcmSHhHRHd5ORPxPhMTvrOO__dOOnlUjMT7xRnwu3nCeIoKmYx5NhgJIbtiS7o1TjQLJWKuUdmy_OYFEVkpwy3B8M=k-no"],"When":"2026-1-3"},{"Name":"Soojennie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLXIZFy5vSdO5OwUwemyCEt7S8OxeB01oVbKScT03ekpQB9Pg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This Korean restaurant is a gem. Every dish is made with incredibly fresh ingredients, and the flavors are clean, vibrant, and perfectly balanced. The presentation is delicate and refined—each plate looks like it was crafted with re