ments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]},{"id":"children","name":"Children","options":[{"name":"Good for kids","enabled":true},{"name":"Has changing table(s)","enabled":true},{"name":"High chairs","enabled":true},{"name":"Kids' menu","enabled":true}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Free street parking","enabled":true},{"name":"On-site parking","enabled":true},{"name":"Parking","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Jesse Stoddard","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUqO_DG5xdKdOv2KwyS43FNpASs43UBbjbOANTfSRzUf_s7MUQY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of the best dining experiences we’ve ever had!\n\nWe celebrated our 21st wedding anniversary and my wife’s birthday at Crabtree Kitchen + Bar, and it could not have been more perfect. From the moment we walked in, the atmosphere was warm, inviting, and elegant… perfect for a special occasion.\n\nThe highlight was the steak, sourced from their own family ranch just outside of town. Truly one of the best steaks I’ve ever had - cooked perfectly, full of flavor, and you could taste the quality. The farm-to-table concept here isn’t just a buzzword, it’s the real deal.\n\nService was outstanding… attentive, knowledgeable, and genuinely friendly. You can tell the staff and leadership take pride in what they do.\n\nBetween the rustic yet refined setting, the amazing food, and the care that went into every detail, Crabtree Kitchen + Bar is a restaurant that sets the bar high. We’ll definitely be back and highly recommend it to anyone looking for an exceptional dining experience in Poulsbo.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0Kaj-0Bhy75bZqxL7y6mdP0F8zQ96ZVnNsHEYxqiCevx1QfZ9aWxd8GVuOxtaXmlWytrzJegi2mNx7OWA3ppx94bbp4sipzixuUqUO5QGCQJPG-R2ADAJiUnUe_PyUPqGw4CSRGyIMnuw=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2J_GugMiBAQMFDIwKz8xYLYhYlgcYyekycenDTdnDgflBi6ZN3SJBXQ-pu6VyHY4GWBCcrhKO2vF4YjdEzO2Do_ABtf_hmgBZHZaZaF8tTyZue5cu9p_lnT6Z-H-3vh1dSw7QDxRKpAgp6=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0kyZwn2r5YH12tfuN6xOdsUw2CsKUdBo01_kRHc6FAo7DElw10HAYJBSVfvGajaKN346zIW846YCo9uE_UqxQz8V0AXS6dCm6orF36PMO0d8QTea5jw8Nd6yIrJd50VB1iAoXjFMLxozw=k-no"],"When":"2025-9-7"},{"Name":"Sonja Kosler","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX-mmD-1FfkWmeMcNYZf_hdwiT4dqkZEdAY7QCyOEKpY1tJf7A6=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We had a group of 14 for Sunday brunch. The menu had food and drink choices to please everyone. The food was excellent. Jackson was an attentive server. We did need the music in our room turned down in order to carry on conversations.\n\nA caution - large group reservations need special arrangements. Groups of 15 or more will not receive individual checks - one total for all.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2EDrEeIT0Kh2H7ayEKXyGe0ymjKZ2WPU1aBKG9AgQ4lrrVtOUYw7QqH6d9TCSJO5Vg4SNuFb8hWBgXbP3xmcjJJGHZCJ-2TuuD62n47ZGZTooc22OFAj722nUODrqlzMh1yVzcuOcFbGyY=k-no"],"When":"2025-10-13"},{"Name":"Käȳ","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWIEZZNzlFLSCpuzhIOJ-FxNxNxLLMIy3jbo4QCmYlVpVrhCqg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a wonderful Valentine's Day dinner here! Our reservation was for 20:30, but due to a system issue, there was a double booking, so we had a short wait of about 30 minutes. The staff was very accommodating and let us enjoy some delicious cocktails at the bar while we waited, which made the time fly by.\n\nI ordered a hibiscus cocktail, which was not only tasty but also beautifully presented with a heart decoration for Valentine's Day—a lovely touch! The special Valentine's dinner menu was fantastic, with every dish tasting absolutely delicious. I wish I had remembered to take a picture of the dessert because the raspberry pudding was uniquely prepared and so good!\n\nThe restaurant has a spacious and sophisticated interior, with an open kitchen where you can watch the chefs in action. There's also a bar and a cozy loft-style waiting area where you can relax with a drink. Plus, they offer a kids' menu, making it a great spot for families, too.\n\nThis place is definitely one of my favorites, and I highly recommend it!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2qPbg7iDxLyN4PqMf2rtPuxO3EJXuoFTbUa3XVTQPvAJo6TlRf1mUBxaqMiV7TyGu8sPj9M0dhppdr6_YfFoGreH6LTaEB6ysOm9nHEGjvEEVUwNloMp3SwR0uZnrDNp1MTEHySw=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1F-zqNlIhDd9SDf9HQ9-oEnAgzuvByd0nkv8UbM6O8nFmLJl87VWOr7xql7RM9wVXP7NfVkEKz9wf1H99cyfV-NTxstbHkyqurHWA_jdvwOPSBU7tyVYznKtR6ImHC1EskM7vx=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0rCYsiOnsAEG0rZhpzP0D5z1AkiTy-nyfBiEVPxX4V47sIzYVbQyjPhvlqAEJa4PxB7NAt4AR-3EIsWwCqqvDnzKL9NbN0n_BeI5U88B1RAPphxncVCIDaY1wiFZagI8ls3iZfPw=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2QuDPSNa2K5djcXrX2rOwIHmmlUVEVPsjVjMdoZ1j2i_JmQSrnVXuBaODFtytXD_haNGeoAtHGvfPDffzPLtYFiBrkRh0gz--QMEbt_ErnrY1oLwcek0e8Xx9q-pIqnpGuo4A=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0lKZTQRBawRQiVTMhXvLx2mhNsXYg0DzTOkAqGt1pPbZr3Bn6pr74v24Zkl4opyyEtaXg0FrvJQVjyK_1saF1z637b62qsmQSReaj6jKuLkh8eEUPLph91_PDzGGm57-u0SWD-tw=k-no"],"When":"2025-2-16"},{"Name":"Barbara James","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJIgMP6MzgoIKeXqHd4CLPHXb2XtHPJd9J9YW4c4zJVOEt9_g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Five very impressed, happy people!   The food was expertly prepared,(our group includes chefs from around the world), the cocktails were excellent (one in our group is a consummate bartender from Seattle) to say nothing of the most superhero waitperson, Rebecca.  She was fun, knowledgeable and attentive but not intrusive.  We had a great experience.  Not cheap, but worth every dollar.  Bravo and thank you.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Philip Corriveau","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVRDoD64-oaY1pdyK2te0rUJjanvf67TJjXWobVevn5NxUIaxMT=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The restaurant is beautiful and they have an excellent wine/beverage program. However, the food was meh. The dishes (and we had a prix fixe) were either dry or lacking in sauce/flavor/balance. We had some pork belly that was dried out (made too far in advance?) a chicken dish that was not salted enough... And rice pudding that had a weird texture and taste... For the price we were not impressed. We will not return.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brittany Kilmer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV1CSrImo9vpm2knloREVuQDksCM-WijYPSWt-7DAOTdFTItv8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had the NY Chicken Fried Steak. Delicious! Such a unique set up. Love the open kitchen!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn23LDwgtSjEshGHVasQuSvRhcCA4oq7jlSEcbF7ZLutt0rUrLjND9CGXVgVHe-7TEVkYforHxiZNFfAuMrcLjwsziSRgfuP96F7TbQkc_Km2oXlpF09YBBh668RTxDmuttFROuX-U4F0MJ7=k-no"],"When":"2026-2-1"},{"Name":"Caryn Kieszling","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUu4qqANklrYwD1ZdbXAejfI1zN0L1xZ_niMPJ8VpET-auePQb9=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent date night or celebration spot. Classy and chic. Food was delicious and drinks were fantastic.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2qHF_lnf3nXpHpnWXukqfvMBtcwoXwDX8-LfHGY0YcKisin05FjGKbX1DQrL8YNYhcSVqbuz6fK0mkhOA7ypVG3fptoX9VRFxSrURqWNGPEBdD1O7zRGNczKWV5NJBnx8bQuw4tqnXbvxu=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1zmyDD_QAm6xVQGqeI94KP3Jk-doVGz89C69d-q4y1ounl6Vu4ZXFEQAjH92T2j9cbScCxubso2eCzOdZS7cc60cGHofVKAZLm0ydLXpjDxFW7Ihz99MfKFbOtjT569XkQJoQtL6U_xtMS=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3epxFYTolTFI-wzj6rlHDiqibACZ3oWmzXMPFZs1VA1