ust hang out with friends.\n\nI tried their 1983 beer while I was here (brewed just 50 feet away!) and it was excellent—smooth, flavorful, and perfectly fresh. The whole Anderson School area is beautiful, with several small pubs, outdoor seating, and even a fantastic whiskey bar called The Shed. Highly recommend exploring the whole property if you come by.\n\nIf you’re in Bothell, this is an absolute must-visit for a laid-back evening. 🍻","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3EBQ7mh3HnhrDQ2LoEvAAAvC3ToKSDN0yKMwxYI9cg-yl9q3w3w-Lh93DMG1FSUaArrvuTnDwBtgvikb2jNcX6LJffhqf1gDsB1y_Lh5-bDdY9z47sOCo8TaAiy1uSkX5CodfVbOpRTesf=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3J_qREWEUwRvgUSF9943HCckscWBYgMmp0HSc9998SH1I-3T4qc576wDmERf-4tH7Nj_N9juStzEsx3N-PyfeVokVLqerHP7suESBDTLDdLq9rRhB9tsasvMg9vWN0VxkjRUBiLREJTU9X=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0tH2sklfga9fSPXNNduapFCnJg2vHAdEEJFoxS4smVLwpyuVwIkh6HszIUeFpxYu2fJuPTitGfn9_j04xCWThfGzHU9Qg9b_DTMBp5dko9l_30jLA5lfnlZSvnK2oZv4Ltm--b4-TapNoA=k-no"],"When":"2025-8-10"},{"Name":"Robert Price","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVYBs4_jMaHmW3hZ_iSY4QNoe-bQO8c9-qY7HrJEH0ceiFc2aUOIQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Experience was good.\nAlthough one of our dishes was a top dollar salad. $20 plus. It came out missing all toppings and dressing.\nTopping were then brought in one at a time. Yet still missing some.\nI feel this salad should of been comped or taken of the ticket or lowered in cost to a plate full of lettuce.  Yet no offer was even made. Id hope in the future that service could be a little more observant and work with guest to have a better experience not just make excuses based on kitchen mistakes or because what was ordered wasnt observed when delivering the food.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jeff","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXq55SeVa9NOEAPNNkud1seoWPAYnroPQkYxnEBEX07YDKNV1w54Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We came here late afternoon for an early dinner and drinks. It wasn’t too busy but was starting to pick up by the time we left. We had a nice time, and it has a nice ambience. We each had a burger with Cajun tots, and they were both delicious. It’s a very spacious place with pool tables and other games. We’ve been here on other occasions, and it gets busy at night, but it was nice to be there when it wasn’t too crowded, but it’s also nice that it gets busy and has a fun atmosphere","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2FwOR1VXQaIfA5vepXj-t0hBRqqYGBToo90nGMszAe_NEf2RYiCmH4Pklmg_8kVeHffUzcg7FXKneLpUHwdr3kIhspZ5QOkdMVype3B1FTJDqCpYPYmuMteqCDlQy6vvSf7Ky-8Q=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2HpEf2lSg2-bDoGAX3E7nNiHo_nmoQgzhyGiN88DQw6q-fTCbjKF1tE1CsTzs2Z6X2our-EblYRizS41p_kfsxUhoORU0Hx-TiSB_UUZIquQxir2VTeHONiS2kohL6hesDfibj=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1FoYWr5Vh_inkVttv8oA-aCmCHnqLV5nW76znqDGoVfmYhwQgUkeJmwW7DpGiXAn6FMYKAegvrKeaF8y2ZgZ8yydS25vFAtmYsJwB8de6JgPmoIutXnJPJabGG3AOO_Mg1DanSvg=k-no"],"When":"2025-3-8"},{"Name":"Jackie Morey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXioByipIslgAZg_vVvNVfrxRETop3pqsOydXKfWuukDN6Osdnx=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The ambience is wonderful, the staff is friendly and helpful, the food was good…but our 4-person group had to wait over 30 minutes to get our food!\n\nThis resulted in one of my friend’s food arriving cold. She rarely complains, but this time she did because her omelette was cold. Thankfully, they prepared a new omelette for her.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn159_j8moGDcRAt9T-NWUYEfoz4YPGeJ5lMDlrSZWpozqhChp-qIc3kOPpaN080JYLHcbtOXXt4AEANLIecDGgwzZBE72g0dhlL3ep_6O2amrHFEIj_HOjyKN_-afYw3OPgO8Lnqg=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3szmguWJu4DDMzYes628TOkDUMcKoyHGBqC4Fjqt2Cg_MWSWZSDAhl69BTCP7xTXUy_DRlW7CI446weyzYSTnmSKHA8tF0uCLQte