r100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very friendly. The menu is not a standard breakfast menu, it's a cut above. The dishes are unique and have some local, fresh ingredients. Their signature dish is the apple cinnamon pancake, which is a but more like French toast in consistency. It was delicious and enough for 2 people, maybe with a side.\n\nService was very friendly with a down home feel.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3g5RmJr4fejXh49f4pWBDeVguOxHty0SSnvSngEAEx2x_RvAlGZbn2ns5qIBO_z8ViqDWB0zbBJvvDlppJX5Fz8sqUj84r854pjL1SrLGhaOuvaZ_U3vn3IDKpeeUsVBzGGnLAwyXh6iif=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2ZzppIxHqNxvEEP0LRIQ8wEO9HUQIBEdTPLfGdXcAtRKgUCUsd-5Eyq3ylYd-dS5OIZSJDhcLl11HztT6IuzmZ5Vd8iGyP7M8qmMnS1WR-vj1zoQGz7Ce3Y9WWRcdJK6Zz_OJ7zeAPdHQ=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3fV0xkhNGq22AVZmNvBiuLsxr0BYTRvLf-EurNQV9HK6MsqTNqW3SmrmEGUYJrw0_Qnh95rizg1G1AScfb-lSa-JGxOPj7mc6MnvcISuAwRDBvnPlurWjASLgH9sAtFvLebgBLvesAo4Kn=k-no"],"When":"2025-8-12"},{"Name":"Nolan Lev-Byrne","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWFOrw-ebamPrL-y8a6EpmGtqpfE9ac42rvvVLJpcUyoaoXlwre=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have no idea how anyone could rate this place anything other than 5 stars. Granted I've only been here twice, both the food and service are well above and beyond any breakfast place I've ever been to. Both Josh and Amy were friendly, gave great recommendations, and we're on top of all the tables they were serving. As someone who has worked in customer service my whole life, this place is a perfect model of what it is to be incredible. I will be coming back here way too often, and keep an eye out for me as the next feature on \"My 600lb life\"","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1jHAehgPPMDfjAzfokS1hi1Syewb_mv1T9emhUi_VgHO_oubAcw3dEaepo565Q-Cc7fqFxx1MWax-hVRumzaFNhfIMhWErDUrEUytafqYoBPGKj2z6TDFH4RELT1loFdjGDZKchi-ZBgzc=k-no"],"When":"2025-9-5"}],"user_reviews