e the bamboo plates and serving dishes - it’s a nice touch! As a vegetarian, I also appreciated that it felt clean and mindful, reducing any concerns about cross-contamination.\n\nI’d definitely consider coming back to try more entrées and explore the rest of the menu. Prices are reasonable and quite pocket-friendly for the quality and flavor they deliver.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3hziilVBb0j0kuEVWTuQWvAfM-mjcfT7WanRQXYvqfsJDLRzRv4A863RVyiFRCf8EGK_xXCYTwhxfaUhILU3QuuLDq5z126Q1LbGIRLhtYvJh836LOXHhgqJ59rGv00yCCxUbhY91PE7qz=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1VSDQbv1J0iiGOtHJZ8PYKWBO2KGulacSVJP4qPFw6tr9JD9tvALhW112vqbJIC1IhfD-fNlbUY7cTX-KGCcI_eDXpP60eNOeGdEdBRUS8lJ047REw_LgUKb0BHbyMpgm9crlJmYM-AEQ=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn35PLZLDg00l-JqGaRVatVpFOVlS4kIi35Ydoi5XBozofbV5nzWpJ6UO_ygcVCW1RvpryFzRNgIRdJgYEfSjiQV79yEtAVcA40GExdnhcwcgzWI_qKz-JZKjpc1VIoTEm5drYXRj3H1-1yz=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0YueIH6ty3My68AcKwQDip6eenAdIYbzmzN-x-2Uo00oic3_N2fJ6VrbMLqw1Qa0qkDZZVKPqkna_EScOoBmWfEANySK5JWCwnasbam37wLQ_0XWb9g8kU4feDhvJg7KiMGdMEZX_P6Nk=k-no"],"When":"2025-10-28"},{"Name":"Sads A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV8tdvByj2hpBY6ftj-Hx5puWe0JkxOvssLuSvEccJOMruKd0ms=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Who rated this place so high? The biriyani was sub par, dry and don’t get me started on the curries. For the price I paid I got so little meat… how is this place running? Did the curries actually taste amazing? No. We got gongura chicken biriyani, Hyderabadi biriyani, palak paneer, butter chicken and a few more items.\nAlso horrible horrible customer service. Never coming back again","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn22gPtM4ZTS2Rzuh9UR7l_qZTKB9RJs61dQu7mg5W1kXDAoWVuQRjEd9bQN5oAu0NaRQxxaEE0fFRp7KGm3wxoqTzp_G4bp46sJS5YoIepF6rYsrmcBhw3mtKwAyaXE7ykAUC31IKUgYkuZ=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gras