d the kids nachos and the steak fajita. The cheese quesadilla is well it’s a simple dish but it was good The french fries are also good. my daughter ordered the nachos and it came with melted cheddar cheese on top which she didn’t care for so we found out that they have a white cheese sauce which they said has jalapeño in it, but I’m really sensitive to spice and I didnt taste the jalapeño so we asked for that instead. this cheese is absolutely amazing. We also dipped out fries in it. I ordered my steak fajita without green peppers instead, I got mushrooms and zucchini and onions and replace the guacamole with avacado.  I’m not too sure like the cut of steak that it comes with, and I’m not quite sure I like the taste of whatever they put the vegetables in but overall with the food that I received tonight along with the atmosphere and how nice employees are five stars hands-down. i’m a huge food critic and it’s really hard to find good Mexican Restaurants. Although they don’t have my favorite dish at this restaurant, they do have dishes that of the restaurants don’t Offer I will definitely be back here to try their chimichangas.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3h5RYoicKXoPxPt2059q8JbFpqBPr5mAooPfrmLG8w83ojXJuRrrH8dMvRYhykRbSsymqqMlJbP0dPa6Ap5gD9h4N1d5Ojj-AaPcjIBR4umdPcSBZPL74-Vjr8SZsS2o4-F4ZR7w=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3BOi3EtYgPqwPwgWrXxoF0qE7xj_hH4euCUR6lQdoyvrxfjAqI9miF0OPiHkE5kJaiAQJ1PAN1yFhtpTBbEVeyBIbH721rOAsMuP49gc3Q7r_o64iF8yw9_W2UEk8F0ohtUEcu=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3kpXSQwyQ8jYuRa-aVGp8W7uEl9WGJQj7wf20kvXKE7xW1Xghp63CaRGVMF5kn5HDOBA_f56xGlwWWAHV09iGIcF_yEhCS5_xrdVRzvBn8jDNWxAYLHOXPKuMW17gGnyDJWej_=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3n2nGAMrf4w797V7V_pESY7xixorwq3-1iES3NCDwu_FqS6fCNZ6JRYtAGdOJ1xy7dwzOmjZB4T78P7cYfC6jwIRfMdbxdV5Hu2FZ9FMMUkraOjB2S6xQACs7Z_KQFQQun434y=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3i-RgquNJIvpKQvyfpDnfHHS2gH