:"Paid parking lot","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Jenn Strange","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXE5FBYUofhhqCxVz42idX5h0KskBEAZ4BiHg8bBO61TwEMwWE=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"There should be a line wrapped around the BLOCK!\nThis food is sensational. Boyfriend and I have driven by this place and talked about going in for a while and I am SO GLAD we did. I am gonna get right to it. We ordered the Cuban sampler to share, everything is fried on this plate, but so light and so crispy. SO FLAVORFUL. I am sorry for screaming but It’s that good. The sauces that came with it I would BATHE IN. They have a garlic aioli that would topple the ranch industry, insanely good. I ordered the Ropa Vieja…… **trembles in a moment of silence** this dish was so flavorful, so succulent, the rice, the beef. All life changing. My lover got a dish that was also really delicious but neither of us could remember the name, really tender ground beef in a super seasoned tomato sauce over rice. Also really delicious.\nTake your own lover here, your best friend, your mortal enemy will BECOME your best friend.\nThis is super food. Prices were more than fair. Service was friendly and warm.\nOH MY GOD, the FLAAAAAAAAAAAN!\nThe flan. Wow wow wow wow.\nSo good!\nGo! Pack up the family, the posse, the gang. Get them all over to Twisted Cuban.\nYou won’t regret it.\nAlso get the Flan. You will quiver.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn14sywNwWJciPD_vhvYVsKSH6JI5w2ZmQzXEgHpljRKR1kYy2gH01SAvb5nm3T23yLvd5dC-meV8khkDnUrB0eM6agV5DqRYgJBSdc5XvMj7bioabYWxqRzTiqiPEAIU0YiRTjT-RHaA_Q=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn18skkYWGp96Q6gELUbGZqWrvyZFa3BuwVJpACz47UAiHAY5Z9xJsBKT7Mewu41wX5ix1dB1ld7mSwmUpyTDZJSXtj9tKQGuF1Z-DWX-DHGsVM50ft9309oge4cWGZho9ODHW7tmZKEtKKT=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0iQUU0CBigQk4xAWz50wv3DgVbxg6Zx9Pn2hyGvgaaOoMw27F_rW6DPQk6ZFifKPrZloCPfxScoAgTHG35Us86HBVzej8TPy8