lso split an order of Maduros which were incredible. The woman who was helping us was welcoming and fast. We all plan to come back!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2lG9lus9YNOCrKKRO9qusNHT-8PKUVrS5AopketN44JNb1si0Zxq36ZlaovdLwqmw11oFGaSatyRDZUf-k0gPSdgyYHsym_NphPK6KYJ0Z9gzpH9c7NgBKs6Rlsw--mAORefsRA33t2tY=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn03noGw9Y5mfFrBiAzPuf5W4kkgjg1Xi0hhUlcjRLVFMzf5Byzx0YPOLgdJfuIDyzUHgLp0XsiRQ4KjgVkoRZIIsKXjRqCL3bDTtGkzg-nQ-YlXfIAEPEuGI_C1EmGOPqHle2Ya5Du3VOZj=k-no"],"When":"2026-2-12"},{"Name":"Stevie Price","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVYE4G0kCdBcLuK5k1HX0QFo-BWP3pVNyJd_hYiF0zr6OTeBp_Hhw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I wish I lived in the area so I could visit this Cafe daily. We enjoyed appetizers, lunch, the best mojito I have ever had and then topped it off with some coffee and cigars. The staff was incredibly kind. The environment was peaceful. The music was vibrant. We played dominoes and ate to our hearts content. Best restaurant experience I've had in a long while.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn19sxC5uIXBvwdI7lYIXyynkwQZuIW-ADo8kBsqob6z3jiZMKM4uSvVNWwJJiH2Du1FsNLr73h_lra_yKqZOyr4GpdhK7znoIyqznxXvnP3t4EqTPkc4ggcATWZrZlNj4aEmI8GVsL3F7k3=k-no"],"When":"2025-9-30"},{"Name":"Scott Hancher","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU8yP9hoXq9kYjWP2eo63Ahh-8brL1I4mySpuj5HWVTm0gtElA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Rustic, comfortable little restaurant tucked on the edge of Woodinville serving excellent Cuban food. The owner is full of energy, and the servers are fun as well. Plated meals are generous in size and don’t forget the sweet Maduros for an appetizer.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0WbnFMpCdfR8MVM7BN-GIKrQv8RrGx4LDrbSK20pi9eSFcI12m44yssAFQvjL6Bh5V1zs0aprnPNRp88GouveAbzcyloDn-8qVyTvEfv4JpXWgBPHmt-z1D-9nsLWzsVWgAYSFGHmFn492=k-no"],"When":"2025-11-26"},{"Name":"Richard Sprague","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUAZ8j40v6t-5FathMZHNN47R1-ZgoEIM43ZiL4k48nZ3CrIY1R=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Pleasant, informal atmosphere with great, original cuban food. We liked the masitas de puerco.  Parking is a little difficult on the busy street, but come early (before 6pm) and you'll have no problems.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1UdVHMkUqO2QmEBKsiCf8MH2ZAwd75rET6gUPjVrE5o0PCN0h8CPj2wFwHk3uMSU_Ji2FkZH48dJSO1tJz1s0nx3Pr_7oi1J9P_-tUlbsJ1KzmKyA4nMmI97TW3Uyd8w1lxcstUe25JslY=k-no"],"When":"2025-11-12"},{"Name":"Ana Garcia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVcbIIBUFZAzr8kv3CHoDy9pNs7jnNMo-6thVqmh7v75OGwb8dW=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Tried the corn fritters which reminded me alot of hush puppies you get with southern cuisine but with more spice. Also loved their pasta dish with ground beef it was delicious.  I had a Cuban mojito which was also very tasty and not too sweet, overall great dining experience the only thing I'd complain about is the parking set up it's tricky and hard to back out","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1sgfJ7ZZ_18VxWvmzDioNKo1YUcr4Qd5DE0OlLLSr4ROIfPoskjvoDJmHyqieZVUsLVBQzhxMA8o0Y_treUD-iSOSrJtrmts04VIYXrQHIbJrSlG_tQ6EqjQD60nh5c9r0tVJ3lGCrK6xB=k-no"],"When":"2025-6-20"},{"Name":"JM Malinchak","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVetj3sDi9fjlfuoACipZG3FTSq8Kwrk1DDuzaB_uBwXPE4vf_0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ordered “Pollo al Ajillo” in which comes with white rice \u0026 black beans for delivery via UberEats. OMG hit the spot, they nailed it. Perfection. I shredded the chicken and fried in olive oil and lime on an iron skillet to make it into “Pollo Vaca Frita”. Delicious.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0trW5-5Js9wqI8DnjBme_CmMvMU7o5jAM8xzuGPdow6EpanSV0xCpmlZLTsH5LSYYQIwJavh9