. There is minimal seating so just be aware this is more of a pick up your food and move somewhere else. I ordered the Burrito with chicken and hubby ordered Street Taco’s (Chicken, Carne Asada and Birria). Honestly everything I had was delicious, the chicken was a little too salty, like the first few bites were insane, then your mouth asked for a drink lol. The Burrito is also nothing to sneeze that bad boy is big and very satisfying. All the tacos were great but hubby’s favorite was the Birria. I have every intention of coming back and begging them to make my burrito a Californian","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3Cm-e9Rkr_oIKz44Jl69osuP_rFD-OPTpw1Wl2tAmL_xn4lb6Uu9AwbKEFtR_E68SKQKOCGFdA4RTJ3cgSSq4jrdt4NvHMF7n3vSuCugktyI69TAv3eFn3G-bC_p2TKbJAr9ogWxqRBVay=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3-vp1B3UdZsfYUqvQzBhUrpr8imXrD5uw2S_WWYu-KCE-9_EdPFq0EIqO83AviGYadrtmj6JyWcPhBVsq6J8T99ZLC68Gw_IBgjInPtASIGbDSXtRMQeHiQq0h4afMtQfWmgMq6kR8JL4=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3is-3g0LLqwPh0aqFaKDYmOBU8XPGjRKQxaYMmem6lRQ0un5o0CtqmKq9YaONjrVBtIia9eXzABhW7dYv27FDPlstT0nfiwP7oakNzh1xTAnhdNCFBraI6-tbgL78OVBDas4D2P_cBLtnu=k-no"],"When":"2025-11-20"},{"Name":"Ian Kingsbury","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVQZfZ5vFgYP5lRBl645d6pXmIcZ_eFWynvR9gSE2qfDJs6ko2Y=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"AMAZING FOOD. The absolute best breakfast burrito I have ever had! ALL DAY BREAKFAST!! The prices are very reasonable. The portions are big and generous. The food quality is top notch. The Birria is also very very good! Everything is so flavorful and prepared with care. The salsa that comes with everything is super good also. Highly recommend this GEM!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Maureen Jones","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVvbsfNoMNVMo8z0FkF0-45bceyFxFKylL8JhNKZrK6w2G3BAbLjw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"All three of my tacos were delicious (carnitas, al pastor and veggie). They were well seasoned and hot, but the veggie taco was by far my favorite. Lots of great flavors, perfectly cooked zucchini and mushrooms.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0HsT2IiCO0DXC9CO8-lwTjy9K0mJYe1LRzkVq_ZfAR2a6jzRSHK5zeK6cd9ICHJgUuj6bYe0dYmgXDyrG_ANhSbc-sdKf_7G8uh5-V8UeebqkmA2ibm2jaOeZdxYFusk8ZzfuaE5eLRPt1=k-no"],"When":"2025-11-27"},{"Name":"Wilfrido Lora Jauregui","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWo8QnpDB8GVR2Yh3I48afCPLzBIlO-rvLSpFRQLG5WYoiSfiDU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Great tacos.\nI had 3 and im stuffed. They had plenty of meat.\nOut of the al pastor carnitas and Asada I'll have to rank carnitas at the top and the asada as 3rd best.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2FxUzVAhRuTsqvNfZ3Yr0hkP1C3C8diclOjHI5ZXXFcuFxrvEVBrV6-Fh4f-vKLc14SQKJISHJNXRctI0ae4nZ8FbO2QbMAfmdX9yOCZy4_SY_mjOdRHkU6oQPhCkrvXt0ccbCKbUvOkQB=k-no"],"When":"2026-1-16"},{"Name":"Kaeley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI5S4tA95-ZUM4FPWH_2cPUaHUqRLPBflTTEUOF2qKmXtGGeIM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Overall: Pretty Good!\n\nThere's no cinnamon in the horchata, neither me or my partner would really call it horchata due to the lack of cinnamon.\n\nThe burrito was pretty okay! For me it was missing something, just not sure what that something was.\n\nPartner really enjoyed the carnitas and lengua. He said the al pastor was good but not as good as others.\n\nAll of their salsa were really good.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1HMdE9MVKE-vhDeIgr4_IEwHQvnnO9kBOq7gdOdw0mFDrPSPOqRO-3XnbtJ9SUFAwYQIvWFFuyWrFl0nqTe33Ltt8oM8hAZLz5t4gGYy-fuYdK8_8Xl7WKqM6Z_OwXhkULcguGosqkd_4=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0ww9GoQ3JkSeoGpxXnIqzJTrEsMbm901eVoA7LHYeulsECO1UTUCl2eRGJ2YS_dothG6teHZTqE0tpYik_-ywVBlXs_Dl1NnSgH0RqPpcudHkYT6sbegRYv_mKJlmtfU2gzJTZCDMDDdwC=k-no","https: