enabled":false}]},{"id":"pets","name":"Pets","options":[{"name":"Dogs allowed outside","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Corinna Fulton","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKuWP3RRbjTkxNeVsXIBZT0WMpbvzcpug3fnxbVpT-HsrQzVA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I got the huli chicken and drunken noodles and OMG so good! I’m usually very picky about my drunken noodles (pad ke mow) and theirs is a little different but amazing. I love all the extra veggies and very generous portions. The sauce station they offer is such a nice touch, we’ll be back!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn106Jq9uW785CKA9jLiCf8K2NZkMx0IHtS6NSp411LsYM5vi3wpVR0B1_cBA-WJiwIG0M6nDptDUuZqSwkcFq3LWpN9MsPBGTaZEZEYXTtrmGxdQNo2ImriJmJ4K9COhpdfyOf_HI3a7eEj=k-no"],"When":"2026-2-13"},{"Name":"CelloMama","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWeyxKQSn04YK8bzmEJR_FX3Cv12e3PI7rNEFC-8E3N66yIKnM6=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We ordered coconut shrimp and spicy sesame chicken, super delish!!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3i6W2puj8T59Ao8QVXgrwlc09DE94rG3m92lTw2P674AZRvmhXZsn9fBxYJ61sDs3PLUQx0FIG4RV4L6vQtfJTzSR9BlOYPiCeTWMh8jqu9T-HrqicPokvv0Lsi8UM4eUpWFIoA8Ib0CIy=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2yNHxx8wLGT8hVRs5Ce4bdoWvAtgfrt6HEIuloSIcH8xwyLkFQdy3eZlwf3875xaa10XuskJMsQdfoxbOhWvFRGdG8nsuUwt2UHz-YDhPGN2q5V_lFwHJdEJM7bjAA3KNNWG20ayv9F8g=k-no"],"When":"2026-3-1"},{"Name":"Joshua Lang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXoSlA49qmyPpK0hcfyKLPRtH3bVZIBgfKEk5Xebi_sMx3gLj9ZFw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been a fan of Buddah Bruddah since going to their food trucks. Their restaurant locations are incredible with the extended menu items. I got the grilled Mahi Mahi and was blown away with the flavors and succulent tasting fish. I also got an order of the Coconut Encrusted Shrimp which is a popular item. Highly recommend!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3thI-1D52y15pKdr3bQ_G0PVgAYqNcVF32p4czCfv25AycTJaqcqSQjjbgZXw3q-gp_72huwK8I3rm8VR1r6gO46e8wO07zVduZMNuUMAnJhW-_JA_FswWWOb8wFE1CjcBg4PULcS9mWOZ=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn15s71wbO4aURWiDBTHz9Tx8cs_IfpN51givsHIScz8kybujYKcb3ncTGXHeU6pvwKj_Dl0kweg81XFrbE0GycrM9J-DG7P-VetdIQUXvEK2gRTwk0CIcTcP5Fr8PZ7uy8dJDT08LH52Os=k-no"],"When":"2025-8-29"},{"Name":"Valerie Normand","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLzJsJvg8Jsvp_puVKcF0UYVsXcMPioHssHcrJSg1-ChGGHTA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We LOVE Buddha Bruddah and are so grateful to have them here in Kenmore! We are regular customers and order takeout nearly every week. We’ve tried most every item on their menu and enjoyed them all. We especially like the Huli Huli Chicken, Mochiko Chicken and Kahlua Pork. And their customer service is excellent!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Wei-ju Wu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVozn9x8OXsI76mD6OFIQJ-wcXLk9Z1_Z2tNzSHGbM2Kr5BYpBRgg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love the food from Buddha Bruddah ever since I had it from the food truck in South Lake Union. This location has the same quality of food, with a larger selection of foods.\nTheir specialty is hawaiian style bbq dishes and I can't decide which I like more. Whether pork, beef or chicken, I like them all and it's just a matter of what I feel like on a given day. They are typically served with Macaroni salad, coleslaw, and rice. You absolutely must try the sauces ! Their dishes are great on their own, but I suggest you try the sauces anyways. They are delicious and come in different spice levels, and 5 star is damn spicy !\nThe food is fairly priced and the portion sizes are pretty large, too. Typically you want to do a take out as the place is not very big, but dining in has the advantage that you can eat the food right when it was made.\nHighly recommended !","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn26nHG8CE0Vmh5mDuEdPxdkLjTpiCd3yOZ8rA-US0ycdoa2K85AsYCoeYwFa0fg3fvP6fYb3XJiPtwWvuJzpOuJHEO4-hkYr6AgT5mDFx81yi74QWwCUtTaUZQ6z_vZn7ffvVAiSQ=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1scK1TVhThiajnU7AzJUxRF5leUkSsOAfL-YLF6NG9gh3j4JpKT18JdEKoSrxWwcbOAiLUdh7CY-xKeq72W6A7c6CwLjyRYphMF5KQP7NgkvbPek3MxfI7b3mNegE1tevMnomd=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1f3WXsnOjmv49-YHmKwKrrT14cUKA_tGzx2ClhEsNigd6ZTjXx_K1lzYEVQwAB4nD_sWUJa5RTNsjZMunjaw4p9oQ4n4zy2kbXRcBVLKSeAHYt0Q9hU_8edj0nuHtSLO3VeLmW3g=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1W2T5hYCjweRogtejq0dx7TRw2SFvfY1icrwov6b4MkxqBo_e_nIEDmY9ZyysuQguCXPORS1vrd7y2Dm9W_LYr0qnnctEMFhI5PQbJvFZofxANRWRh8DjEmlhTzG0ICL4GIxU=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn14tweVrL8Cr6KdmcewY3pdC1ypZfXN9La61MPfKKyulsYhKxrc5fqWalMs0If680msdtIy_0ps2Mujr493n1pxIhIKWXKAlzRvK_bVC3Rm22I5RQQPZQV_hI1RL9VXw6elRIfv4w=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2kiC4ZzfhY1nUe0S_aA9SlZvasIjtNLodL5R73--hDRyaOrU1snYSZ9e8JleF3-Fmo-46ZrImYiHrt4kPqgl7U4QW0SEyf1Jej_HhJU3WzKWPXI6EDHnEBMre0ctM-2lbgCntv=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2dopBjkZ3o2d29Y_aKKCYUyKKlwTkslM0E-wKM8PEDTLCNAu1BPPMkH8-t70y2vAMgcURguYH_MPw4ybfxeodt1c8P8YEg7S0Cy5IY6y4eCdcxPqX1DlNlUgHuBcZrFuPVWk7PaQ=k-no"],"When":"2023-1-25"},{"Name":"NorahM","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWFSp02uQud0COQ_hwH0oCyKGV3dSg_sQFp4Hz7MAcnkRlNHuY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is the only place I get tasty Hawaiian-style chicken teriyaki that is not offered by our neighborhood teriyaki joints. The website take-out is convenient and flexible for me to substitute/add side choices. They’re generous with  portions and variety of free pick-up sauces. Just try it! All staff are friendly with the aloha spirit!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Austin Johnson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI-17kipoXwmJuQrNS9nqSCstMLwedMtEUMQgVA993IXJxf1gpq=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Totally recommend this place. I've been eyeballing it for a year+ and finally decided that today was the day. I asked the woman (Patty I believe? She says she usually caters too) at the counter what she would recommend for a first timer there and I picked the huli huli chicken. The chicken is out of this world. It's moist and tender and the sauce has so much flavor. One of the owners was in as well and we had a quick small chat and he gave me a dessert on the house.\n\nPeople are friendly, service is exceptional, food is fast and delicious, price is fair for what you get. What more do you want? My kinda restaurant.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Hannah Bressler","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIVBw3GmIPJL1JYNcY2IKRXxkA5ZpaiQEREh0H0iOwrW-t2o6w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Small, family owned business with great Hawaiian-Thai fusion. At this point I have had most of the items on the menu and I have not been disappointed with anything. Everything is really tasty and the portions are great for sharing. The location is small with a few sit down tables at the restaurant.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
