learly old so it was a bit annoying.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0-R_wh9UVowBJns79YDOAALIrzbwwQJVcD6xiXVaWjQ-SXdzREoOC3vRy_bcSgqQLBpLqwnBH4up_PfhxUOq7WSm6tR8AkIly8dEI9Dsmxx5Nw_whiFojpuatSG9xVxW2YZQn8U9Pi5Ow=k-no"],"When":"2026-3-7"},{"Name":"Clint Moyer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLuVq7P1DnctH-mUAc5B0rDkPH9rCZKlGOkXoCMHrVN3xtkvg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of our favorite places on the Eastside. They have several locations with a consistent vibe. Al dente perfection with a ton of pasta options. Always good seating, clean, and excellent service. The cashier will eagerly deliver the pasta sermon to those who ask.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2J7090LYc2gd-hPp3x0hdV_dvtMOm9t2d_C3iv4VVGMdUWtbbijEUBjUKK3bg0Ab-1HFS8rn0tZO9qJYk5njHmYiovMvW9mZZ7oAPioJ3EhqeNPsdwBaJTmv-wvHkbKSbVu5V8OqhWVT6l=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2mFqNKFdH6SQPfe-RsHS1quOeqE6Ne-ROM-OdGCMuG-jukvMQC34o7s-fr_sxzcgIXCzDWH3I8BZLCUs_BIMCHUod5vH3b1e1hQv2CHwroH4rwfcY2a15PU8tbwC1HAeZ4shLB-V7Xlwsn=k-no"],"When":"2026-2-15"},{"Name":"ساغر هنرزاده","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUI_NvgL4f-6F5V6q2Gq5VDtXNV_FURVLUS2rm8EB8PXZLT6ZCEtQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The pasta was absolutely incredible—rich, flavorful, and cooked to perfection. The vibe of the place is amazing, with a cozy and welcoming atmosphere. One of the staff even complimented my hair, which made the experience even more friendly and personal. Great food, wonderful people, and a spot I’ll definitely be coming back to!\"","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1pxUhNZ__YH9Xobp8Ix0OkYuUJxIomQrgPGU5Yaorju2oeNGF6WjhqJAUfmh-pimHuGUinKwigQI0pJnZtJawjlcVncTgHjZ_VADvIkshn5aroDRxGTu3RxVlc_CJO6yrxqOh_cbRIbrqS=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0-1tCs3YWRlbsia9GRj8IGliVc-Y4rQg9SDrOgXEJsLpAM96DvcPYDcMMKSaqtjRedJOg11FrBHDtanX